query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  s.name as service_name,
  p.smshubPrice,
  p.ourPrice,
  a.name as api_name
FROM prices p
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
WHERE p.apiId = 1
LIMIT 10
